Package ca.corefacility.bioinformatics.irida.model.sample

Class Sample

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.corefacility.bioinformatics.irida.model.IridaRepresentationModel
      • ca.corefacility.bioinformatics.irida.model.sample.Sample
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IridaThing, MutableIridaThing, RemoteSynchronizable, Timestamped<java.lang.Long>, java.lang.Comparable<Sample>
    @Entity
public class Sample
extends IridaRepresentationModel
implements MutableIridaThing, java.lang.Comparable<Sample>, RemoteSynchronizable
    A biological sample. Each sample may correspond to many files. A Sample comprises of many attributes. The attributes assigned to a Sample correspond to the NCBI Pathogen BioSample attributes. See BioSample Attributes: Package Pathogen for more information.
